statements: SELECT * FROM WebsiteTraffic
SELECT ID, Timestamp, UserIP FROM WebsiteTraffic
SELECT PageVisited, InteractionType FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE UserIP='192.168.1.1'
SELECT * FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE PageVisited='Homepage' AND InteractionType='Click'
SELECT PageVisited, COUNT(*) AS VisitCount FROM WebsiteTraffic GROUP BY PageVisited ORDER BY VisitCount DESC
SELECT * FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE ID = 1;
SELECT PageVisited, InteractionType FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE UserIP = '192.168.1.1';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS TotalVisits FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE PageVisited LIKE '%homepage%';
SELECT UserIP, COUNT(*) AS TotalInteractions FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE InteractionType = 'Click' GROUP BY UserIP ORDER BY TotalInteractions DESC;
SELECT PageVisited, COUNT(*) AS VisitCount FROM WebsiteTraffic GROUP BY PageVisited HAVING VisitCount > 10 ORDER BY VisitCount DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, page_visited, timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_visits FROM website_traffic WHERE page_visited = 'Homepage';
SELECT user_id, MAX(timestamp) AS latest_interaction FROM user_interactions GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT * FROM user_interactions ORDER BY action_taken ASC, timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE user_id = 2 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;
SELECT user_id, page_visited, timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE page_visited LIKE '%home%' ORDER BY timestamp;
SELECT u.user_id, u.action_taken, w.page_visited, w.timestamp FROM user_interactions u JOIN website_traffic w ON u.user_id = w.user_id ORDER BY w.timestamp DESC;

SELECT u.user_id, AVG(DATEDIFF(w.timestamp, u.timestamp)) AS avg_days_between_interactions FROM user_interactions u JOIN website_traffic w ON u.user_id = w.user_id GROUP BY u.user_id HAVING avg_days_between_interactions > 10;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE id = 1;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_traffic ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'click';
SELECT product_id, interaction_type FROM shopping_experience WHERE user_id = 5;
SELECT * FROM shopping_experience ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE page_visited = 'Homepage';
SELECT id, visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_traffic WHERE timestamp >= '2022-07-01';
SELECT DISTINCT visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_traffic WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-07-01' AND '2022-07-31';
SELECT * FROM user_interactions WHERE user_id = 123 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(product_id) AS total_products FROM shopping_experience GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_products > 3;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;
SELECT page_url, visitor_ip FROM website_traffic WHERE interaction_type = 'click';
SELECT user_id, interaction_timestamp FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'like' ORDER BY interaction_timestamp;
SELECT product_id, quantity FROM shopping_cart WHERE quantity > 1;
SELECT username, email FROM user_profiles WHERE last_login >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM user_interactions GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_interactions > 5;
SELECT username, email FROM user_profiles WHERE registration_date >= '2022-01-01' AND last_login < '2022-10-01';
SELECT page_url, visitor_ip, visit_timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE interaction_type = 'click' ORDER BY visit_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, product_id, quantity, added_to_cart_timestamp FROM shopping_cart ORDER BY added_to_cart_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM website_users;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM website_users WHERE age > 30;
SELECT user_id, username FROM website_users ORDER BY username ASC;
SELECT user_id, email FROM website_users WHERE username LIKE 'A%';
SELECT user_id, email, age FROM website_users WHERE age IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM website_users WHERE age > 30;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM website_users ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT page_name, COUNT(*) AS page_views_count FROM page_views GROUP BY page_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 10;
SELECT ph.user_id, ph.product_name, ph.price, pi.quantity FROM purchase_history ph INNER JOIN cart_items pi ON ph.user_id = pi.user_id;
SELECT rp.product_name, rp.recommendation_score FROM recommend_products rp WHERE recommendation_score > 4.5 ORDER BY recommendation_score DESC;
